; Regression test for issue #1609: Auto-balancing of transactions of no value (BZ#537)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1609
;
; When a balance assertion (= $10.00) results in a zero-value difference,
; the auto-balancing posting should be treated as $0.00 rather than raising
; "Only one posting with null amount allowed per transaction".

2011/01/01 Depreciation
  Assets  $10.00
  Expenses

2011/02/01 Depreciation
  Assets  $0.00
  Expenses

2011/03/01 Depreciation
  Assets  = $10.00
  Expenses

test bal
              $10.00  Assets
             $-10.00  Expenses
--------------------
                   0
end test
